message: “Give hope to the ones who have no hope at all. Stand up for the ones who can't stand at all." -jon foreman   Text FREE to 91999 to Donate. All donations go towards the emergency needs of human trafficking survivors in the U.S. and our 3-day Law Enforcement Human Trafficking Investigations Class. Together we can make a difference. #lawenforcement #helperase #childtrafficking
